<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes primarily maintain the alliance rather than fire. <i>Salix jepsonii </i>sprouts rapidly from damage.</div>
